[SN]TITLE[SN]
Ardingly gas leak crash driver disqualified

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man has been disqualified from driving for 22 months after he crashed his car into a house in West Sussex and caused a gas leak.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
